title: "Synoptic Context Management: Graph-Augmented Bi-Temporal Memory and Semantic-Temporal Modulation in Edge LLMs"
version: "5.1.0"
date-released: 2026-03-15
url: "https://github.com/zinthose/ccma-edge-architecture"
keywords:
  - edge-llm
